{"id": 534, "genre": 1001, "title": "小时候做过哪些不堪回首的事？", "description": "想起来就想把脸埋进土里。", "record_count": 19403, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160607194613ZXGFNcUmCVvkadwr.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-09-27T01:07:14Z", "options": [{"id": 14592, "content": "全班静悄悄上早自习，我很气愤还一本正经的对老师大声说xxx抄卷我把他卷撕了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 220831}, {"id": 13313, "content": "原来大家都有不堪回首的事儿，心情豁然开朗，不说也罢( ´▽` )ﾉ", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 204369}, {"id": 14593, "content": "吃饭时噎到了，然后自己跑到厕所等死(⊙_⊙)", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 220251}, {"id": 23553, "content": "吃狗粮", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 292913}, {"id": 13314, "content": "把枕头毛巾包在头上当做自己有满头长发?", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 205044}, {"id": 14338, "content": "冬天把脚放在煤火上取暖，把袜子烧个洞。用铁碗炒鸡蛋！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 219507}, {"id": 13827, "content": "把羊粑粑当作糖豆放嘴里", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 211959}, {"id": 14083, "content": "和姐姐演青蛇白蛇，和妹妹演妈妈女儿。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 215412}, {"id": 17156, "content": "以为会考上清华或北大", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 248427}, {"id": 13573, "content": "小时候明明是男的，非得打扮成女孩子。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 209141}, {"id": 13829, "content": "大概9岁的时候，向小女孩表白，，，，很多人面前，，，，", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 212135}, {"id": 15109, "content": "在大街上小便", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 231498}, {"id": 17670, "content": "暗恋好几个女孩，没有一个说上一句话", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 255032}, {"id": 14343, "content": "那时候天真的要死遇到什么都好奇过去摸一摸。结果???", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 216798}, {"id": 14855, "content": "小时候 吹牛说自己多牛", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 226038}, {"id": 23559, "content": "给比我大的学生让座人家连句谢谢都没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 292772}, {"id": 29959, "content": "不堪回首的事儿太多了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 294200}, {"id": 13577, "content": "小时候把小丁丁塞进墨水瓶，结果看着被染成深蓝色的小丁丁，吓毁了，洗了N多天才恢复原色╮(╯_╰)╭", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 169698}, {"id": 13322, "content": "对着镜子自言自语。在脑海里模拟场景然后把中二的羞耻度爆表的台词说出来。我这是什么病。（其实现在仍然这样）", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 205131}, {"id": 14091, "content": "自己用沙子做个马桶，然后向里面撒尿，在当成是像怪兽一样，把马桶毁了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 211943}, {"id": 17163, "content": "在网吧，被老爸抓住，强行收拾一波", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 252079}, {"id": 13324, "content": "修毛时被父亲看到?", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 205170}, {"id": 14092, "content": "写作文感叹人生，现在看了觉得蛋疼", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 215536}, {"id": 13837, "content": "和姐姐玩亲亲", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 212208}, {"id": 14605, "content": "强迫弟弟和妹妹举行婚礼，把他们关小黑屋让他们学武侠片亲亲。（捂脸逃～）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 223912}, {"id": 13326, "content": "看动漫电影里的超级英雄们，顿时激情四射，拿起了老妈三千多的围巾滚下了沙丘……", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 200849}, {"id": 14094, "content": "村里姐姐们处在发育期对性充满好奇于是怂恿我们小孩男女搭档睡觉，我让一个男生压我身上好几分钟，但实在什么感觉都没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 214676}, {"id": 13327, "content": "上学迟到了，怕到哭", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 205229}, {"id": 13583, "content": "扔鞭炮进厕所里，结果里面的人没提裤子就跑出来了", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 209229}, {"id": 79887, "content": "不堪回首就莫再提了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 614458}, {"id": 15887, "content": "我小时候住平房，在院子里洗澡的时候被路人看到来着……", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 237999}, {"id": 16143, "content": "吃鼻屎，还为了不被家长看见躲起来吃！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 241472}, {"id": 13328, "content": "当众背诵英语课文 结果 第一次见这么多人 脑子就放空了 丢脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 205226}, {"id": 14864, "content": "吸笔管  吸～?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 185657}, {"id": 13329, "content": "曾经趁爸爸睡的正沉时，将自己的臭袜子发在他的鼻子上。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 205252}, {"id": 14609, "content": "觉得自己是外星人，他们一定看得到我的一言一行！直至今日…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 224052}, {"id": 13330, "content": "觉得自己也能孵小鸡，硬是拿几床被子盖住一枚鸡蛋坐了大半天。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 205277}, {"id": 15122, "content": "玩跑跑抓 拿着扫把冲进女厕 摔倒了 脸朝地", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 231622}, {"id": 13331, "content": "以为自己会飞 从床上飞到几米远的梳妆台拿梳子…头上摔了个包", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 205278}, {"id": 13332, "content": "没戴眼镜走错课室了orz", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 202465}, {"id": 13844, "content": "好朋友搬家过后，翻墙去把他家，把他家当成聚点，后来被发现，领着我见爸妈，后来差点被爸妈打死", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 212300}, {"id": 13333, "content": "喜欢同桌，上课时老假装没带书，就为了和她一起看", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 205314}, {"id": 14869, "content": "刚学会骑自行车   在大雨中骑   整个人都被浇湿了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 227436}, {"id": 19221, "content": "打喷嚏喷，鼻涕喷了数学书一整页，没有纸擦！我是菇凉。；（", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 263163}, {"id": 13334, "content": "连续门特7次就为了看看我的极限是哪里", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 205324}, {"id": 14102, "content": "撒尿活泥巴", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 173528}, {"id": 13335, "content": "年少的我为自己单相思的女友写了一大堆的情话，现在回头再看狂笑不止", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 205393}, {"id": 13847, "content": "小时候和女孩纸脱光了在被子里抱在一起滚啊滚算不？", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 212333}, {"id": 13592, "content": "把两把钥匙插到了插线板的火线端和零线端", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 208725}, {"id": 13593, "content": "用鞭炮爆牛粪", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 122296}]}